BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Mt3f17w0B5UQvBO8S278b
SUMMARY:Immigration is Not Invasion: Dean's Luminaries in Law Series with I
	lya Somin
DTSTAMP:20260318T234513Z
DTSTART:20260319T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle University School of Law’s Luminaries in Law Series con
	tinues with a timely and thought-provoking conversation titled Immigration
	 Is Not Invasion\, featuring renowned constitutional law scholar Ilya Somi
	n.\n\n \n\nIn this special lunchtime event\, Professor Somin will be inter
	viewed by Anthony E. Varona\, Dean of Seattle University School of Law\, a
	nd Andrew Siegel\, Professor of Law. Together\, they will explore Professo
	r Somin’s scholarship challenging the increasingly common framing of immig
	ration as an “invasion\,” examining its constitutional\, historical\, and 
	democratic implications.\n\n \n\nThe discussion will engage questions at t
	he intersection of immigration law\, constitutional structure\, political 
	rhetoric\, and civil liberties\, offering insight into how legal doctrine 
	and public discourse shape immigration policy and democratic values. Drawi
	ng on their respective expertise\, Dean Varona and Professor Siegel will g
	uide a wide-ranging conversation designed to illuminate one of the most pr
	essing legal and societal debates of our time.\n\n \n\nStudents\, faculty\
	, and members of the broader legal community are invited to attend this en
	gaging installment of the Luminaries in Law series.\n\n \n\nDate: March 19
	th\n\nLocation: Room C5\, Sullivan Hall\n\nTime: 12:00 PM to 12:50 PM.\n\n
	https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/immigration-is-not-invasion-
	dean-s-luminaries-in-law-series-with-ilya-somin/18260246/2026-03-19T00\n\n
	From SEAtoday - Learning & Education
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/immigration-is-not-invasi
	on-dean-s-luminaries-in-law-series-with-ilya-somin/18260246/2026-03-19T00
LOCATION:Sullivan Hall\, C5\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-learning
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Learning & Education
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
