UID:atj18hBL7ntVNb4xra4hi
SUMMARY:Wine party
DTSTAMP:20260318T234514Z
DTSTART:20260320T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Downtown (0.5 miles S)\n\nDress up and taste wine\, drink signa
	ture cocktails\, meet winemakers\, eat gourmet appetizers\, play retro vid
	eo games\, dance to DJ music\, and hear musicians at $174 The New Vintage 
	at Lotte Hotel\, 811 5th Ave. in Seattle. Must be age 21+. This event is p
	art of Taste Washington.\n\nhttps://www.tastewashington.org/the-new-vintag
	e/\n\nFrom Events12 Seattle
URL:https://www.tastewashington.org/the-new-vintage/
