DTSTAMP:20260318T234514Z
DTSTART:20260321T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description Join us for planting at the Debays Slough Reserve o
	n Saturday\, March 21st. Join us 9am-noon to continue restoring the ripari
	an zone of DeBay's Slough off Francis Road in Mount Vernon. Please dress f
	or the weather\; we will provide work gloves and tools\, and closed-toe sh
