BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:oiVCGEInrkA1wqPMAMjL7
SUMMARY:Business After Hours: VMFH
DTSTAMP:20260318T234514Z
DTSTART:20260326T003000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description    Networking is a vital component of career succes
	s\, with 80% of professionals considering it essential and nearly 100% bel
