	5 • Grades 6–8 Teams of 1–4 students Projects can include trifolds\, poste
	rs\, models\, or demonstrations Awards will be given in each division. ━━━
	━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ HOW TO PARTICIPATE ✔ Submit a team project \\(Grades 3–8\\
	) ✔ Attend and explore projects\, interactive math games & activities ━━━━
	━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ ⏳ IMPORTANT DEADLINES Registration: March 15\, 2026 Project
